  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to better understand the factors associated with mortality and
      identify potentially preventable causes of death in neonates who die after receiving health
      care. As a result, an improved neonatal mortality classification system may be defined.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
